Before editing catalog, Sanity schemas, or partner product flows, read:

- `/ai_context/01_PROJECT_HANDOVER.md` (partner flow)
- `/ai_context/02_ARCHITECTURE_MAP.md` (Sanity vs Supabase split)

Critical rules:

- Only **approved** bouquets/products appear on the public catalog.
- Partner products may require admin moderation before going live.
- Partner auth uses Supabase session (`lib/partner/`); catalog documents live in Sanity.
- Do not invent prices, stock, or delivery times in copy — use content skills for wording.

For **product or blog copy**, use `.cursor/skills/flower-content-writer/` or `.cursor/skills/blog-content-writer/` — not new rules here.
